* ``Python`` >= 3.6.0
* ``opencv-python``
* ``shapely``
* ``onnxruntime``

* Works on Linux, Windows, MacOS

# 使用方式

- Pypi
- [HTTP API](https://github.com/chenwei-zhao/captcha-api)

## Pypi

### 从 Pypi 安装

```bash
pip install captcha-recognizer
```

